FBIS4-548 "drafr071_a_94016" FBIS-AFR-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Fighting Between Army, RPF Continues in Kigali Fighting Between Army, RPF Continues in Kigali RPF Claims Control in North EA1204205594 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in English to Rwanda 1900 GMT 12 Apr 94 EA1204205594 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura English BFN [Excerpt] Reports reaching us say heavy fighting took place yesterday and today in the areas of Byumba, Mutara, and Ruhengeri. In all these places, our forces inflicted heavy casualties on the government forces. In the Mutara zone, the towns of Nyagatare and Gabiro are under the control of Rwandan Patriotic Front soldiers. [passage omitted]
